00:34:54,563 --> 00:34:57,364
'An official announcement
may be expected shortly.

495
00:34:57,477 --> 00:35:00,321
'Meanwhile, some of the residents
of the invaded area

496
00:35:00,430 --> 00:35:05,508
'are taking steps to curb what they
